Alembic migrations live in this folder.

Quickstart (MySQL):
- Set `DATABASE_URL_SYNC` in `backend/.env` to a `mysql+pymysql://...` URL
- Run: `alembic upgrade head`

Note:
- The application runtime uses async SQLAlchemy (`DATABASE_URL`, e.g. `mysql+asyncmy://...`).
- Alembic uses a sync driver URL for migrations (`DATABASE_URL_SYNC`).

